text: Al-Ahly or Al-Ahli () is the Arabic for "national", and may refer to: ;Basketball * Al Ahly (basketball club), Egypt * Al-Ahli Jeddah (basketball), Saudi Arabia ;Football * Al Ahly SC, Egypt * Al-Ahly Benghazi, Libya * Al-Ahly Tripoli, Libya * Al-Ahly Shendi, Sudan * Al-Ahli SC (Saida), Lebanon * Al Ahli SC (Doha), Qatar * Al-Ahli SC (Jeddah), Saudi Arabia * Al-Ahli (Amman), Jordan * Al-Ahli Khartoum, Sudan * Al-Ahli SC (Wad Medani), Sudan * Al-Ahli Club (Manama), Bahrain * Al-Ahli Club (Dubai), United Arab Emirates * Al-Ahli Club Sana'a, Yemen, Sana'a * Al-Ahli Taizz SC, Yemen, Taizz ;Other organizations * Al Bank Al Ahli Al Omani, an Omani bank merged with BankMuscat in 1993
title: Al-Ahly
